{
  "id": "user.toolbox.sub",
  "name": "实用工具箱合集",
  "description": "福利吧签到 + TestFlight 自动加入，统一管理配置",
  "author": "@ader90520 & @Yuheng0101",
  "icon": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leiyiyan/resource/main/icons/pyy.png",
  "repo": "https://github.com/ader90520/fulibaqiandao",
  "apps": [
    {
      "id": "fuba_sign",
      "name": "福利吧签到",
      "author": "@ader90520",
      "repo": "https://github.com/ader90520/fulibaqiandao",
      "icons": [
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leiyiyan/resource/main/icons/pyy.png",
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leiyiyan/resource/main/icons/pyy.png"
      ],
      "keys": [
        "fuba_cookie",
        "fuba_username",
        "fuba_domain",
        "fuba_last_sign_date",
        "fuba_continuous_days",
        "fuba_total_days",
        "fuba_points"
      ],
      "settings": [
        {
          "id": "fuba_domain",
          "name": "福利吧域名",
          "val": "www.wnflb2023.com",
          "type": "select",
          "options": [
            { "name": "wnflb2023.com", "val": "www.wnflb2023.com" },
            { "name": "wnflb00.com", "val": "www.wnflb00.com" },
            { "name": "wnflb99.com", "val": "www.wnflb99.com" }
          ],
          "desc": "选择福利吧访问域名"
        },
        {
          "id": "fuba_cookie",
          "name": "福利吧Cookie",
          "val": "",
          "type": "textarea",
          "autoGrow": true,
          "placeholder": "通过重写规则自动获取",
          "desc": "已配置自动获取，无需手动填写"
        },
        {
          "id": "fuba_username",
          "name": "福利吧用户名",
          "val": "",
          "type": "text",
          "placeholder": "通过重写规则自动获取",
          "desc": "已配置自动获取，无需手动填写"
        },
        {
          "id": "@fuba.auto_get",
          "name": "自动获取状态",
          "val": false,
          "type": "boolean",
          "desc": "显示是否已自动获取Cookie和用户名"
        },
        {
          "id": "fuba_last_sign_date",
          "name": "最后签到日期",
          "val": "",
          "type": "text",
          "placeholder": "自动记录",
          "desc": "脚本自动记录的最后成功签到日期（格式：2026年04月03日）",
          "readonly": true
        },
        {
          "id": "fuba_continuous_days",
          "name": "连续签到天数",
          "val": "0",
          "type": "number",
          "placeholder": "0",
          "desc": "脚本自动记录的连续签到天数",
          "readonly": true
        },
        {
          "id": "fuba_total_days",
          "name": "总签到天数",
          "val": "0",
          "type": "number",
          "placeholder": "0",
          "desc": "脚本自动记录的累计签到总天数",
          "readonly": true
        },
        {
          "id": "fuba_points",
          "name": "当前积分",
          "val": "0",
          "type": "text",
          "placeholder": "自动获取",
          "desc": "脚本自动更新的当前积分",
          "readonly": true
        }
      ],
      "scripts": [
        {
          "name": "福利吧签到脚本",
          "script": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ader90520/QuantumultX/refs/heads/main/Stripts/myScripts/fuba/fuba.js"
        }
      ],
      "desc_html": [
        "<div style='padding: 10px; background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 5px;'>",
        "<p><strong>⚠️ 重要提示</strong></p>",
        "<ul>",
        "<li>获取成功后建议禁用获取规则，避免重复触发</li>",
        "<li>Cookie有效期通常为1-3个月，过期需重新获取</li>",
        "<li>请勿分享您的Cookie信息，确保账号安全</li>",
        "<li>如遇签到失败，请检查Cookie是否失效并重新获取</li>",
        "<li>统计字段由脚本自动维护，无需手动修改</li>",
        "</ul>",
        "</div>"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "testflight_auto_join",
      "name": "TestFlight 自动加入",
      "author": "@Yuheng0101 (基于 @MuTu888 原脚本)",
      "repo": "https://github.com/Yuheng0101/X",
      "icons": [
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/githubdulong/Script/master/Images/testflight.png",
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/githubdulong/Script/master/Images/testflight.png"
      ],
      "keys": [
        "tf_key",
        "tf_session_id",
        "tf_session_digest",
        "tf_request_id",
        "tf_apple_store_front",
        "tf_apple_ta_device",
        "tf_apple_amd_m",
        "tf_apple_device_model",
        "tf_user_agent",
        "tf_app_ids",
        "tf_loon_count",
        "tf_interval"
      ],
      "settings": [
        {
          "id": "tf_key",
          "name": "🔑 Key",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "账号标识，通常从抓取中获得（/accounts/ 后的部分）",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_session_id",
          "name": "📇 Session ID",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "x-session-id 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_session_digest",
          "name": "🔐 Session Digest",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "x-session-digest 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_request_id",
          "name": "🆔 Request ID",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "x-request-id 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_apple_store_front",
          "name": "🏬 Store Front",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "x-apple-store-front 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_apple_ta_device",
          "name": "📱 TA Device",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "x-apple-ta-device 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_apple_amd_m",
          "name": "💻 AMD M",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "x-apple-amd-m 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_apple_device_model",
          "name": "📟 Device Model",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "x-apple-device-model 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_user_agent",
          "name": "🌐 User Agent",
          "type": "text",
          "desc": "User-Agent 请求头",
          "val": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_app_ids",
          "name": "📦 应用 ID 列表",
          "type": "textarea",
          "desc": "格式：appid#status ，多个用英文逗号分隔。status=0 未加入，1 已加入。脚本会自动管理，通常无需手动修改。",
          "val": "",
          "autoGrow": true
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_loon_count",
          "name": "🔄 循环尝试次数",
          "type": "number",
          "desc": "每次定时任务内对同一个应用尝试加入的次数，默认 1",
          "val": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "tf_interval",
          "name": "⏱️ 尝试间隔（秒）",
          "type": "number",
          "desc": "每次循环尝试之间的等待秒数，默认 0",
          "val": 0
        }
      ],
      "scripts": [
        {
          "name": "TestFlight 自动加入脚本",
          "script": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Yuheng0101/X/main/Tasks/AutoJoinTF.js"
        }
      ],
      "desc_html": [
        "<div style='padding: 10px; background: #e7f3ff; border: 1px solid #b8daff; border-radius: 5px;'>",
        "<p><strong>📌 使用说明</strong></p>",
        "<ul>",
        "<li>首次使用需开启 HTTP 请求抓取（配置详见脚本头部注释）</li>",
        "<li>打开 TestFlight APP 或分享链接即可自动捕获参数</li>",
        "<li>定时任务会自动监控并加入尚未参与的应用</li>",
        "<li>大部分参数由脚本自动写入，无需手动干预</li>",
        "<li>如需修改尝试次数或间隔，可在此调整对应数值</li>",
        "</ul>",
        "</div>"
      ]
    }
  ]
}